  "body": "The current strategy in next only works in the context of verbose reporting. At present if a migrations fails when logging is silent (e.g. the tests) we get no information about what happened. \r\n\r\nWe need to patch this as stop-gap pending efforts to move all the deployment error reporting over to `truffle-contract`\r\n",
